\hat{\sigma}^2_{ML} = \displaystyle\frac{1}{N}\sum_{k=1}^{N}(x_k-\hat{\mu})^2
E(\hat{\sigma}^2_{ML}) = \displaystyle\frac{1}{N}\sum_{k=1}^{N}E[(x_k-\hat{\mu})^2] = \displaystyle\frac{N-1}{N}\sigma^2
