E[(x_k-\hat{\mu})^2] = \sigma^2
E(\hat{\sigma}^2_{ML}) = \displaystyle\frac{1}{N}\sum_{k=1}^{N}E[(x_k-\hat{\mu})^2] = \displaystyle\frac{N*\sigma^2}{N} = \sigma^2
